# This folder is for tax-related documents
#
# Suggested contents:
#   - T2125 (Statement of Business Activities) copies
#   - Annual income summaries
#   - GST/HST returns (if registered)
#   - CRA correspondence
#   - Tax preparer documents
#
# At year end, you can generate reports:
#   hledger -f accounting/main.journal incomestatement -p 2025 > taxes/2025-income-statement.txt
#   hledger -f accounting/main.journal balance expenses -p 2025 > taxes/2025-expenses.txt
